The paper focuses on the assurance of machine learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also covers the different stages of the machine learning lifecycle, which involves software engineering practices (cs.SE). The methods discussed in the paper involve statistical and machine learning techniques (cs.LG), as well as security and safety considerations (cs.CR) and system engineering principles (cs.SY).
